overview: Bree Haze is cleaning the kitchen in her black leather miniskirt when the moving boys, Victor and Sabby, carry her heavy white couch. Bree insists on giving them a little extra for their trouble. Evelina Darling is still in training and very eager to show her bosses what she's capable of. The slender European brunette is completely willing to take on extra work and the boys Matt Bird and Victor are all too willing to offer it up. Haley Hill sips idly on a fruity beverage by the pool as her friend Choky Ice passes by, and he brings an extra package - Vinny Star. Fanboy Toby sits alongside porn star Sofi Goldfinger for a selfie... but Sofi is all riled up! Things quickly escalade as Sofi keeps on the same track as she was post-picture break and that means one thing for lucky Toby: Sex! Trusted Thomas Stone jumps in too and at three they make a horny cast and crew party.
title: Dipping Two Straws
